      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PURE MOUSE (1) used the rails draw to advantage to get home last time at this track and distance (22.59) after forging to the front and leading throughout, scoring by a nose. The one to beat again off the inside draw. CAMARO ROSE (5) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish second, beaten a nose, (22.60) at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Bold showing expected. EXCITING FORTE (2) was unwanted in betting when starting from the same box but ran very well, finishing in the minors over 400m at this track in a Maiden in 22.82. Good beginner and aided by a handy draw. Harder here but expected to feature again. MAJOR FORTE (6) is last start winner who looks one of the chances.",
